SUMMARY:Suggestion Box
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\nTo see upcoming events more easily\, use the Calendar view = https://www.meetup.com/pdxgames/events/calendar/\n\nThis is a space for suggestions and ideas -- no matter how wild\, crazy\, or impractical -- and complaints are cool too.\n\nIf you have an idea or request\, simply leave a comment.\nFeel free to reply and add more.\n\nWe can also use this space for news or random postings.\n\nHowever if you want a more general response -- from the whole community\, as opposed to the leadership menagerie -- you should start a 'Discussion' at https://www.meetup.com/pdxgames/discussions/
