SUMMARY:Board Games @ Guardian Games
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\nCome join us for Board Game Open Play at Guardian Games every Sunday from 12-6pm\, hosted by Alex from [Might I Suggest A Game](https://www.instagram.com/might.i.suggest.a.game/)! Learn the game of the week\, play from our free demo library\, or bring your own for a fun afternoon of good friends and good games :)\n\nThe game of the week is TBD!
