SUMMARY:Monday Night Game Event
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\nCome have fun with people\, as we learn new games\, rediscovered classics and enjoy the best of the best\, that modern board games can give.\n\nBoard games are plenty\, feel free to bring some -- usually a couple of us do\, and the Venue has a large library as well.\n\nWe play mostly lighter and middle weight games\, but sometimes heavier ones -- from party games to euros.\n\nPlease ask questions in the comments\, and let people know what board games you will bring and/or want to play.
